{"tid":1719254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Locobike] 今早發現大量單車被人私鎖 想市民幫手解鎖","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T12:11:32.000Z","uid":22556,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc19a475522d8b61af975bfc2ad0c75b26e7601","tid":1719254,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"[切勿私鎖，嚴正呼籲]<br />\n尋晚到今朝，各區由粉嶺到沙田一帶，將軍澳(屯門唔洗講)，好多車都比不明生物私鎖左。我哋loco team用盡方法拎返啲車，如果大家見到私鎖車，我哋唔介意大家用任何合法途徑拎返架車，架車鎖唔到都好過比人鎖住用唔到。我哋開鎖唔係比不明生物一個人用。<br />\n另外大家用完車，請一定要鎖車，咁先更新到架車個即時位置，唔係下手揾唔到車。如果急用車，因為系統未好返，請參考呢個post <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Qehx9v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Qehx9v&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=634f38a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Qehx9v</a><br />\nP.S睇相要睇到尾，有踩車教學，用testing account skip第二步。<br />\n#CLS #科學園都有私鎖 #主場 #想點 #嬲到震 #我哋office係你架車樓上望住 #咪咁癲 #wearewatchingyou"},{"pid":"1775a9cb5de1c9ea761866609288c50bdae24556","tid":1719254,"uid":211814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"直接幫佢鎖多個鎖，然後貼張紙警告佢解番個鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d92fdbf5daca288b14dcfcc391106eb2962182","tid":1719254,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1775a9cb5de1c9ea761866609288c50bdae24556","tid":1719254,"uid":211814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"直接幫佢鎖多個鎖，然後貼張紙警告佢解番個鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"有用how<br />\n入錢比loco個app最有用"},{"pid":"8dc7c00e06f546f0166c8f98629c45159e4f07a8","tid":1719254,"uid":211814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56d92fdbf5daca288b14dcfcc391106eb2962182","tid":1719254,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1775a9cb5de1c9ea761866609288c50bdae24556","tid":1719254,"uid":211814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"